<p>As the final bell rang, Chad skipped off into the sunset, his laughter echoing through the empty halls. Derek knew that he had changed Chad's life forever, for better or for worse. And as he walked home that day, he couldn't shake the feeling that he had unlocked something deep within himself as well.</p></div>

