<p>Now, dear William, I urge you to consider this offer carefully. A once-in-a-lifetime chance to possess these priceless figurines and complete your scammer's paradise. Do not let this opportunity slip away like Homestar slipping on a banana peel, for it may never come knocking on your inbox again.</p>
