    line-height: 1.6;">Story about Joanna de la Vega, Laurel Lance (from The Arrow tv show) &amp; Nicolas. <br/>Nicolas description for references: 20 years old. 1m78, and a bit overweight, short skipy brown hairs &amp; brown eyes behind glasses. He doesn’t grow past his shyness &amp; awkward way.<br/>Joanna has known Nicolas since a few years now and is happy to see him now working for CNRI. This is their itw meeting. Set before season 1.</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
    background-color: #fff3e6;
