<p>And suddenly, fate seemed to smile upon him – a door miraculously swung open, lights pouring out from the building like a beacon in the darkness. With no time to ponder the consequences, Kevin dove inside and slammed the door behind him, instantly realizing that whatever was waiting on the other side of the threshold could be no more appealing than the latest chorus of massive breasts he’d found himself in…</p>
<p>But what he saw upon entering was the ultimate final challenge – an international event which took breast admiration beyond the boundaries of the known universe. Kevin stood in a bustling room filled with international competitors – all of them buxom women in various stages of undress – attended by people in lab coats with clipboards and rulers. The room hummed with excitement and salacious intent, as the voluptuous representatives from around the world jostled for position on the panorama of pulchritudinous pectorals.</p>
<p>Kevin froze for a moment, unsure of what to do next. He could turn and face the ex-marine and his wrath or risk his sanity by staying amongst the worldwide gathering of the planet’s most abundant bosoms..</p>
<p>With resolve in his heart and entirely too much bare skin on display, Kevin marched towards the stage. If he was going down, he figured, he might as well go down surrounded by the very best massive breasts the world had to offer.</p></div>

